<div data-collapse="medium" data-animation="default" data-duration="400" data-contain="1" class="w-nav navigation-bar"><div class="w-container"><a href="/" class="w-nav-brand brand-link w--current"><h1 class="brand-text">ONgikar</h1></a><nav role="navigation" class="w-nav-menu navigation-menu"><a href="/" class="w-nav-link navigation-link w--current" style="max-width: 728px;">Home</a><a href="/contact" class="w-nav-link navigation-link" style="max-width: 728px;">Contact</a></nav><div class="w-nav-button hamburger-button"><div class="w-icon-nav-menu"></div></div></div><div class="w-nav-overlay" data-wf-ignore=""></div></div><div class="w-section hero-section centered"><div data-ix="new-interaction" class="w-container"><h1 data-ix="fade-in-bottom-page-loads" class="hero-heading" style="opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px) translateZ(0px); transition: opacity 1000ms, transform 1000ms;">PROMISES are meant to be kept</h1><div data-ix="fade-in-bottom-page-loads" class="hero-subheading" style="opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px) translateZ(0px); transition: opacity 1000ms, transform 1000ms;">... so lets change our culture of breaking promises ...</div><div data-ix="fade-in-bottom-page-loads" style="opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px) translateZ(0px); transition: opacity 1000ms, transform 1000ms;"><a href="#" class="button">sign up</a><a href="#" class="hollow-button all-caps">Learn more</a></div></div></div><div class="w-section section"><div class="w-container"><div class="section-title-group"><h2 class="section-heading centered">what IS ONGIKAR ?</h2><div class="section-subheading center"><strong>How many times people make promise to us and just forget to keep it ?</strong> <br><br>Your friend told you to treat you at razzak and never showed up<br>the shop owner told you he will deliver your order by monday, and didn't pick up the phone until wednesday<br>she told you she would teach you basic photography, but couldn't make timE<br><br><span class="brand-text">Ongikar is the awesome platform to track, remind &amp; <strong xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><em>MAKE</em></strong> them keep the promises !</span></div></div><div class="w-row"><div class="w-col w-col-4"><div class="white-box"><img src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a224_feather-15-white.svg" class="grid-image"><h3>INIT PROMISES</h3><p>create promises</p></div></div><div class="w-col w-col-4"><div class="white-box"><img width="210" src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a225_feather2-17-white.svg" class="grid-image"><h3>TRACK PROGRESS</h3><p>add participants and keep track</p></div></div><div class="w-col w-col-4"><div class="white-box"><img src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a226_feather2-22-white.svg" class="grid-image"><h3>KEEPER/BREAKER</h3><p>rate positive / negative promisers</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="w-section section accent"><div class="w-container"><div class="section-title-group"><h2 class="section-heading centered white">HOW IT WORKES</h2><div class="section-subheading center off-white">THE SECRET OF KEEPING A PROMISE IS KEEPING IT DOCUMENTED AND MAKE IT TRANSPARENT TO ALL THE PARTICIPANTS. THATS WHAT ONGIKAR DOES.</div></div><div class="w-row"><div class="w-col w-col-6"><div class="white-box transparent"><img src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a221_bEtrJY1dRKG9jrOPiImg_over-ganges.jpg" class="fullwidth-image"><h3 class="white-text">TRACK YOUR PROMISES</h3><p class="white-text">Track each of the promises they make to you. From personal to business promises.</p><a href="#" class="hollow-button">Learn more</a></div></div><div class="w-col w-col-6"><div class="white-box transparent"><img src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a228_photo-1416400639808-f41f0c149b09.jpg" class="fullwidth-image"><h3 class="white-text">RATE KEEPERS / BREAKER</h3><p class="white-text">Reward them with points if its a keeper. Else make them ashamed if its a breaker.</p><a href="#" class="hollow-button all-caps">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="w-section footer"><div class="w-container"><div class="w-row"><div class="w-col w-col-4 spc"><h5>ABOUT ONGIKAR</h5><p>We are the angry victims of the promise breakers. We believe the habit of breaking casual promises somehow got injected inside the Bengali culture. We took the vow to change the culture. We want to make em understand, a promise is never to be broken.</p></div><div class="w-col w-col-4 spc"><h5>useful links</h5><a href="#" class="footer-link">some links</a></div><div class="w-col w-col-4"><h5>social</h5><div class="w-clearfix footer-link-wrapper"><img width="20" src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1fa_social-18.svg" class="info-icon"><a href="#" class="footer-link with-icon">Twitter</a></div><div class="w-clearfix footer-link-wrapper"><img width="20" src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1e9_social-03.svg" class="info-icon"><a href="#" class="footer-link with-icon">Facebook</a></div><div class="w-clearfix footer-link-wrapper"><img width="20" src="http://uploads.webflow.com/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1d3/571ef3d63db91b9047b9a1eb_social-06.svg" class="info-icon"><a href="#" class="footer-link with-icon">Google</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="w-section footer center"><div class="w-container"><div class="footer-text">Â© Ongikar 2016</div></div></div>
